"When creating a client a {project_name} Client Representation is returned with details about the created client, including a registration access token.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: source/securing_apps/topics/client-registration.adoc:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "To create a client do a HTTP POST with the SAML Entity Descriptor to `/realms/<realm>/clients-registrations/saml2-entity-descriptor`.\n"
